The paper discusses the Raven I and Raven II surgical robots, which are used as open research platforms for robotic surgery research. This topic falls under the field of robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV) which are often used in robotic surgery research. Additionally, the Raven robots are used for surgical procedures, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
